So y’all know every now and then I take a break frm social media …. For personal reasons… MS and a few other things I battle can put me in a space where I dnt want to be online…. But I have to because that’s how I been paying my bills the last 10 yrs 😂
I believe we all have a purpose and things happen for a reason. So I’m not gonna lie after some deep therapy I’ve come to realize God gives his hardest battles to his strongest soldiers and babyyyyyy well here I am 🤗
So I’m going to share from here on out everything every week because I know my story will help someone and help them to keep going. 
So I’m not gonna write an essay here I’m just gonna show up more online. Make sure you subscribe to my YouTube channel as I drop my Vlog tonight on my crazy 😝 life ….Click the link in my bio to SUBSCRIBE

To all of my new followers & friends allow me to reintroduce myself ❤️
My name is Raven, I’m 32 years young. Here you will see the behind the scenes on entrepreneurship and my roller coaster life. I’m just here to share my story & journey 🤗

I learned that in todays world of business you have to be different and stand out but yet still have a purpose. If there is no purpose I promise you, it won’t last long. 

✨What I’ve learned in Business …
1. Consistency is 💰 
2. Hard work beats talent.
3. Trust yourself.
4. If not now then when? 
5. Think different. Out the box.
